title: Tabarsu
text: Tabarsu (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Ţabarsū) is a village in <a href="Kelardasht-e%20Sharqi%20Rural%20District">Kelardasht-e Sharqi Rural District</a>, <a href="Kelardasht%20District">Kelardasht District</a>, <a href="Chalus%20County">Chalus County</a>, <a href="Mazandaran%20Province">Mazandaran Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 207, in 60 families.
